creator: Peanut App Ltd
descriptionHtml:
Peanut makes it easy to meet, chat and learn from like-minded women.

MEET - Swipe and connect with like-minded women nearby.
CHAT - Chat and create group conversations.
JOIN - Join groups relating to specific interests or neighborhoods.
SHARE - Ask questions, create polls and share advice across topics.

Join our community of women today!

-----------------------

Here's what our women say:

"Peanut means a network, it means meeting women who are going through your same experiences. It means supporting one another through this adventure." - Lauren

"It's no longer necessary to feel isolated during fertility, pregnancy or motherhood — the Peanut app is a reminder that community is possible and we don’t have to do it alone." - Sophie

"I wish I knew about Peanut sooner as it's so important to surround yourself with like-minded women during those overwhelming moments." - Lydia

"Being able to connect with other women, get advice and share struggles has been a huge gift and I have Peanut to thank." - Sarah
descriptionShort: The social network connecting women across fertility and motherhood.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
This week we’re rolling out some brand new features that we think you’ll love. Including a mute keywords function that removes related posts from your feed (yep, you can use this for COVID-19!). Plus, we’ve made it easier than ever to invite your friends to join Peanut, and squashed some pesky bugs.

Are you lovin' Peanut? Don't forget to rate us in the App Store!

Simply type the @ symbol into a comment box or post title and type the name of the person you’d like to tag or respond to. And voilà, they’ll be notified instantly!

Are you lovin' Peanut? Don't forget to rate us in Google Play!

You asked, we listened… Mentions are here! Whether you want to share important advice or show someone a funny meme, you can now mention other users in posts and comments. Are you lovin' Peanut? Don't forget to rate us in Google Play!

title: Peanut - Meet other Women

creator: Peanut App Ltd
descriptionHtml:
Peanut makes it easy to meet, chat and learn from like-minded women.

MEET - Swipe and connect with like-minded women nearby.
CHAT - Start conversations and video chats with your connections.
JOIN - Join groups relating to specific interests or neighborhoods.
SHARE - Ask questions, create polls and share advice across topics.

Join our community of women today!

-----------------------

Here's what our women say:

"Peanut means a network, it means meeting women who are going through your same experiences. It means supporting one another through this adventure." - Lauren

"It's no longer necessary to feel isolated during fertility, pregnancy or motherhood — the Peanut app is a reminder that community is possible and we don’t have to do it alone." - Sophie

"I wish I knew about Peanut sooner as it's so important to surround yourself with like-minded women during those overwhelming moments." - Lydia

"Being able to connect with other women, get advice and share struggles has been a huge gift and I have Peanut to thank." - Sarah

Simply type the @ symbol into a comment box or post title and type the name of the person you’d like to tag or respond to. And voilà, they’ll be notified instantly!

Are you lovin' Peanut? Don't forget to rate us in Google Play!

title: Peanut - Meet other Women

creator: Peanut App Ltd
descriptionHtml:
Peanut makes it easy to meet, chat and learn from like-minded women.

MEET - Swipe and connect with like-minded women nearby.
CHAT - Start conversations and video chats with your connections.
JOIN - Join groups relating to specific interests or neighborhoods.
SHARE - Ask questions, create polls and share advice across topics.

Join our community of women today!

-----------------------

Here's what our women say:

"Peanut means a network, it means meeting women who are going through your same experiences. It means supporting one another through this adventure." - Lauren

"It's no longer necessary to feel isolated during fertility, pregnancy or motherhood — the Peanut app is a reminder that community is possible and we don’t have to do it alone." - Sophie

"I wish I knew about Peanut sooner as it's so important to surround yourself with like-minded women during those overwhelming moments." - Lydia

"Being able to connect with other women, get advice and share struggles has been a huge gift and I have Peanut to thank." - Sarah
descriptionShort: Support, connection and community throughout all stages of motherhood. ⚡️

title: Peanut - Meet other Women

creator: Peanut App Ltd
descriptionHtml:
Looking to meet new friends and get advice? We’ve got you. Peanut is the app connecting like-minded women throughout all stages of motherhood.

We provide a safe space for women who are trying to get pregnant, expecting, or already a mum to build friendships, ask questions, and find support.

Introducing you to women nearby who are at a similar stage in life, Peanut provides access to a community of women who are there to listen, share information and offer valuable advice.

Whether it’s understanding fertility, IVF, adoption, pregnancy, first years or nursery and beyond, Peanut is a place to connect with women like you.

The app is completely free to download and use! 🙌

Meet 👋
● Meet like-minded women nearby and swipe to send a wave.

Chat 💬
● Chat with your connections and start video calls.

Groups 👭
● Explore groups and find communities with common interests.

Share 👀
● Ask questions and search advice across meaningful topics.

Here’s what our women say:

“It's no longer necessary to feel isolated during fertility, pregnancy or parenting — the Peanut app is a reminder that community is possible and we don’t have to do it alone." - Sophie

“Without Peanut, I wouldn’t have met my best friend. I’ll always recommend it to anyone looking for mum friends!” - Lydia

“Peanut is my favorite pregnancy app. It’s made it so easy to meet friends near me while on maternity leave and find support as a first time mom.” - Lauren

“Having fertility issues and TTC is lonely and daunting. To find a safe space where people who are in my boat can meet and support one another is exactly what I need.” - Danielle

“Peanut is a social network where you can talk about everything from baby names and breastfeeding to ovulation and miscarriage support, it’s an important reminder that you’re not alone.” - Emmy

Here’s what the press say:

“New mothers can feel isolated, but now technology has come to their rescue.” (The Times)
“Peanut serves as a reminder that you’re not alone; in both infertility and isolation.” (Harper’s Bazaar)
“The first digital community that offers a community of support through shared experience.” (Brit + Co)
“Peanut is a welcome sign that change is afoot, and the internet is finally growing up.” (Refinery29)
descriptionShort: Support, connection and community throughout all stages of motherhood. ⚡️

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Breaking news: Peanut now supports video! That’s right, we’ve launched video so that you have a safe space to share those cute (and not so cute) moments at home. Simply tap the camera icon in a post or reply to share or film a 20 second snippet!

Are you lovin' Peanut? Don't forget to rate us!

creator: Peanut App Ltd
descriptionHtml:
Looking to meet new friends and get advice? We’ve got you. Peanut is the app connecting like-minded women throughout all stages of motherhood.

Meet 👋
● Meet like-minded women nearby and swipe to send a wave.

Chat 💬
● Chat with your connections and start video calls.

Groups 👭
● Explore groups and find communities with common interests.

Share 👀
● Ask questions and search advice across meaningful topics.

We provide a safe space for women who are trying to get pregnant, expecting, or already a mum to build friendships, ask questions, and find support.

Introducing you to women nearby who are at a similar stage in life, Peanut provides access to a community of women who are there to listen, share information and offer valuable advice.

Whether it’s understanding fertility, IVF, adoption, pregnancy, first years or nursery and beyond, Peanut is a place to connect with women like you.

The app is completely free to download and use! 🙌

Here’s what our women say:

“It's no longer necessary to feel isolated during fertility, pregnancy or parenting — the Peanut app is a reminder that community is possible and we don’t have to do it alone." - Sophie

“Without Peanut, I wouldn’t have met my best friend. I’ll always recommend it to anyone looking for mum friends!” - Lydia

"Peanut is my favorite pregnancy app. It’s made it so easy to meet friends near me while on maternity leave and find support as a first time mom.” - Lauren

"Having fertility issues and TTC is lonely and daunting. To find a safe space where people who are in my boat can meet and support one another is exactly what I need.” - Danielle

“Peanut is a social network where you can talk about everything from baby names and breastfeeding to ovulation and miscarriage support, it’s an important reminder that you’re not alone.” - Emmy

Here’s what the press say:

“New mothers can feel isolated, but now technology has come to their rescue.” (The Times)
“Peanut serves as a reminder that you’re not alone; in both infertility and isolation.” (Harper’s Bazaar)
“The first digital community that offers a community of support through shared experience.” (Brit + Co)
“Peanut is a welcome sign that change is afoot, and the internet is finally growing up.” (Refinery29)

We provide a safe space for women who are moms, pregnant, or trying to conceive to build friendships, ask questions, and find support.

Introducing you to women nearby who are at a similar stage in life, Peanut provides access to a community of women who are there to listen, share information and offer valuable advice.

Whether it’s understanding fertility, IVF, adoption, pregnancy, first years or kindergarten and beyond, Peanut is a place to connect with women like you.

The app is completely free to download and use! 🙌

Meet 👋
● Meet like-minded women nearby and swipe to send a wave.

Chat 💬
● Chat with your connections and start video calls.

Groups 👭
● Explore groups and find communities with common interests.

Share 👀
● Ask questions and search advice across meaningful topics.

Here’s what our women say:

“It's no longer necessary to feel isolated during fertility, pregnancy or motherhood — the Peanut app is a reminder that community is possible and we don’t have to do it alone." - Sophie

“Without Peanut, I wouldn’t have met my best friend. I’ll always recommend it to anyone looking for mom friends!” - Lydia

"Peanut is my favorite pregnancy app. It’s made it so easy to meet friends near me and find support as a first time mama.” - Lauren

"Having fertility issues and TTC is lonely and daunting. To find a space where people who are in my boat can meet and support one another is exactly what I need.” - Danielle

“Peanut is a safe space to talk about everything from baby names and breastfeeding to miscarriage and IVF, it’s an important reminder that you’re not alone.” - Emmy
descriptionShort: Support, connection and community throughout all stages of motherhood. ⚡️

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
We've just introduced Topics, a brand new way to customize your Peanut experience and navigate to more meaningful content and communities. The premise is simple. If you’re interested in a Topic, follow it. If you’re not, just unfollow. This helps us show you more relevant content! Head to your feed settings to customize yours.

Are you lovin' Peanut? Don't forget to rate us in Google Play!

title: Peanut - Meet other Women

creator: Peanut App Ltd
descriptionHtml:
Looking to meet new friends and get advice? We’ve got you. Peanut is the app connecting like-minded women throughout all stages of motherhood.

We provide a safe space for women who are moms, pregnant, or trying to conceive to build friendships, ask questions, and find support.

Introducing you to women nearby who are at a similar stage in life, Peanut provides access to a community of women who are there to listen, share information and offer valuable advice.

title: Peanut - Meet other Women

creator: Peanut App Ltd
descriptionHtml:
Looking to meet new friends and get advice? We’ve got you. Peanut is the app connecting like-minded women throughout all stages of motherhood.

We provide a safe space for women who are moms, pregnant, or trying to conceive to build friendships, ask questions, and find support.

Introducing you to women nearby who are at a similar stage in life, Peanut provides access to a community of women who are there to listen, share information and offer valuable advice.

Whether it’s understanding fertility, IVF, adoption, pregnancy, first years or kindergarten and beyond, Peanut is a place to connect with women like you.

The app is completely free to download and use! 🙌

Meet 👋
● Meet like-minded women nearby and swipe to send a wave.

Chat 💬
● Talk, start video calls, and join live audio conversations.

Groups 👭
● Explore groups and find communities with common interests.

Share 👀
● Ask questions and search advice across meaningful topics.

Here’s what our women say:

“It's no longer necessary to feel isolated during fertility, pregnancy or motherhood — the Peanut app is a reminder that community is possible and we don’t have to do it alone." - Sophie

“Without Peanut, I wouldn’t have met my best friend. I’ll always recommend it to anyone looking for mom friends!” - Lydia

"Peanut is my favorite pregnancy app. It’s made it so easy to meet friends near me and find support as a first time mama.” - Lauren

"Having fertility issues and TTC is lonely and daunting. To find a space where people who are in my boat can meet and support one another is exactly what I need.” - Danielle

“Peanut is a safe space to talk about everything from baby names and breastfeeding to miscarriage and IVF, it’s an important reminder that you’re not alone.” - Emmy

title: Peanut - Meet other Women

creator: Peanut App Ltd
descriptionHtml:
Welcome to Peanut, the app connecting women throughout all stages of womanhood. 💌

Over 2 million women have joined Peanut to connect, ask questions and find support. Whether you’re navigating fertility, pregnancy, motherhood or menopause, the app provides access to a community who are there to listen, share information and offer valuable advice.

Finding friends at a similar stage in life is easy on Peanut. The app is free to download and use and always will be!

INTRODUCING, OUR FEATURES

👋 Meet: Discover women nearby who are at a similar stage in life
💬 Chat: Talk to your matches via chat or video call
👭 Groups: Join groups and find communities with common interests
💁‍♀️ Share: Ask questions, search advice and share stories across meaningful topics
🎙️ Pods: Join live audio conversations hosted by experts

WE’RE SAFETY FIRST

Safety is embedded throughout the Peanut experience to encourage caring, supportive and purposeful connections.

🤚All profiles on Peanut are verified with selfie verification
🤚We have a zero tolerance policy towards abusive behavior of any kind
🤚Sensitive content filters mask content that may be triggering
🤚Topics put you in control of the content you want to see
🤚Anti-hate badges are awarded to those who hold others accountable

THE LOVE IS REAL

With over 2M+ women using the app, Peanut has become a coveted destination for women looking to find community.

❤️“It's no longer necessary to feel isolated during womanhood — the Peanut app is a reminder that community is possible and we don’t have to do it alone." - Sophie

❤️“Without Peanut, I wouldn’t have met my best friend. I’ll always recommend it to anyone looking for friends!” - Lydia

❤️"Peanut is my favorite app. It’s made it so easy to meet friends near me and find support as a first time mama.” - Lauren

❤️"Having fertility issues is lonely and daunting. To find a space where people who are in my boat can meet and support one another is exactly what I need.” - Feluke

❤️“Peanut is a safe space to talk about everything from menopause and midlife to sex and relationships, it’s an important reminder that you’re not alone.” - Emmy
descriptionShort: Support, connection and community throughout all stages of motherhood. ⚡️

Team Peanut x

Welcome to Peanut, a safe space to connect with women who are at a similar stage in life. ❤️

Over 2.5M women have joined Peanut to connect, ask questions and find support throughout fertility, pregnancy, motherhood and menopause. The app provides access to a community who are there to listen, share information and offer valuable advice.

Whether you’re looking for fertility friends, mom friends, baby names, breastfeeding tips or menopause advice, we’ve got you.


The Peanut app is
free to download and always will be!



THE SOCIAL NETWORK, FOR WOMEN

👋
Meet: New friends are just a swipe away‒nearby or at a similar stage in life/
💬
Chat: Talk to your matches via chat or video call.
👭
Groups: Join support groups and find communities with common interests.
💁‍♀️
Share: Ask questions and share advice across topics like breastfeeding, parenting, baby development, ovulation, getting pregnant, menopause and more!
🎙️
Pods: Join live audio conversations with experts across fertility, TTC, pregnancy, motherhood, and menopause.


A SAFE SPACE

Safety is embedded throughout the Peanut social app to encourage caring, supportive and purposeful connections for every woman.

✔️ All profiles on Peanut are checked with selfie verification
✔️ We have a zero tolerance policy towards abusive behavior of any kind
✔️ Sensitive content filters mask content that may be triggering
✔️ Topics put you in control of the content you want to see
✔️ Anti-hate badges are awarded to those who hold others accountable

---

Privacy Policy: https://www.peanut-app.io/privacy
Terms of Use: https://www.peanut-app.io/terms
Community Guidelines: https://www.peanut-app.io/community-guidelines
App Support: feedback@teampeanut.com
descriptionShort: Meet new friends–from fertility and pregnancy to motherhood and menopause.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: Small tweaks behind the scenes this week. Instead of boring you with the details, we want to give a shoutout to the women who are tired every single night but stay up scrolling through their phones. You are our people.

title: Peanut: Make New Friends & Find Support

creator: Peanut App Ltd
descriptionHtml:
Welcome to Peanut, a safe space for women to connect, meet, and find support. ❤️

Over 2.5 million women have joined Peanut to connect, ask questions and find support.

Whether you’re navigating fertility, pregnancy, motherhood, or menopause, the Peanut app for women provides access to a community who are there to listen, share information and offer valuable advice.

Finding friends at a similar stage in life is easy with Peanut. Mom friends, first-time moms, fertility friends, menopause friends, pregnancy pals, or any women looking to meet new friends!

The Peanut app is
free to download and always will be!


SOCIAL NETWORKING, FOR WOMEN

👩‍⚕️
Expert advice: Experts to help with fertility, TTC, pregnancy, motherhood, and menopause
😎
Incognito: Post ‘embarrassing’ questions anonymously
👶

📱

🧊

🏳️‍🌈
LGBTQIA+: A safe space for everyone
🤰

🚫
Mute: Easily hide topics you don’t want to see
📣
Topics: Discuss a range of topics with no judgment: breastfeeding, parenting, baby development, ovulation, getting pregnant, menopause… whatever you want!


FEATURES

👋
Meet: New friends are just a swipe away ‒ nearby and at a similar stage in life
💬
Chat: Talk to your matches via chat or video call
👭
Groups: Join support groups with common interests, experiences, or locations
💁‍♀️
Share: Ask questions, find advice and share stories across meaningful topics
🎙️
Pods: Join live audio conversations on a range of topics


A SAFE SPACE FOR ALL WOMEN

Safety is embedded throughout the Peanut social app to encourage caring, supportive and purposeful connections for every woman.

✔️ All profiles on Peanut are checked with selfie verification
✔️ We have a zero tolerance policy towards abusive behavior of any kind

🚫

Whether you’re looking for fertility friends, mom friends, baby names, breastfeeding tips or menopause advice, we’ve got you.

Peanut is
free to download and use. If you're looking to speed up the friend-finding process, you can pay to see who has waved at you or keep swiping to find a match for free. The prices may vary per country and are clearly displayed in the app.


THE SOCIAL NETWORK, FOR WOMEN

👋
Meet: New friends are just a swipe away‒nearby or at a similar stage in life/
💬
Chat: Talk to your matches via chat or video call.
👭
Groups: Join support groups and find communities with common interests.
💁‍♀️
Share: Ask questions and share advice across topics like breastfeeding, parenting, baby development, ovulation, getting pregnant, menopause and more!
🎙️
Pods: Join live audio conversations with experts across fertility, TTC, pregnancy, motherhood, and menopause.


A SAFE SPACE

Safety is embedded throughout the Peanut social app to encourage caring, supportive and purposeful connections for every woman.

✔️ All profiles on Peanut are checked with selfie verification
✔️ We have a zero tolerance policy towards abusive behavior of any kind
✔️ Sensitive content filters mask content that may be triggering
✔️ Topics put you in control of the content you want to see
✔️ Anti-hate badges are awarded to those who hold others accountable

---

Community Guidelines: https://www.peanut-app.io/community-guidelines

title: Peanut App: Find Mum Friends

creator: Peanut App Ltd
descriptionHtml:
YOU’RE NOT ALONE

Every day, millions of women turn to Peanut to connect throughout all stages of motherhood. Created for and by women, the app is a safe space to meet women nearby and have meaningful conversations. Whether you’re trying for a baby, pregnant, or a new mother, Peanut provides access to a community who are there to listen, share information and offer valuable advice.

With recent accolades including Fast Company’s Most Innovative Companies 2023, TIME100’s Most Influential Companies 2022 and Apple’s Trend of the Year 2021, Peanut has become a coveted social network for women looking to connect, ask questions and find support.

FIND FRIENDS WHO GET IT

👋 Meet: New friends are just a swipe away‒meet people nearby who are at a similar life stage.

💬 Chat: Talk to your connections via chat or video call.

👭 Groups: Join support groups and find communities with common interests.

💁‍♀️ Share: Ask questions and share advice across pregnancy, motherhood, baby and more.

🎙️ Pods: Join live audio conversations with real-life experts.

WE’VE GOT YOU

Safety is embedded throughout the app to encourage caring, supportive and purposeful connections.

✔️ All profiles on Peanut are checked with selfie verification

✔️ We have a zero tolerance policy towards abusive behaviour of any kind

✔️ Sensitive content filters mask content that may be triggering

✔️ Topics put you in control of the content you want to see

✔️ Anti-hate badges are awarded to those who hold others accountable

WORD ON THE STREET

“The matchmaking app for modern motherhood” - Forbes

“A welcoming community where everyone can have their say” - HuffPost

"An app for mothers who missed out on dating apps” - New York Times

“This app is a game-changer if you want to make more mum friends” - Woman’s Day

—————————————————————————————————

Peanut is free to download and use. If you're looking to speed up the friend-finding process, you can pay purchase a Peanut Plus subscription or keep swiping to find friends for free. The prices may vary per country and are clearly displayed in the app.

Privacy Policy: https://www.peanut-app.io/privacy

Terms of Use: https://www.peanut-app.io/terms

Community Guidelines: https://www.peanut-app.io/community-guidelines

App Support: feedback@teampeanut.com
descriptionShort: Meet new friends during fertility, pregnancy and motherhood.

title:
Peanut App: Find Mum Friends
6.79.1-b25758

creator: Peanut App Ltd
descriptionHtml:
**YOU’RE NOT ALONE. FIND MUM FRIENDS.**

Welcome to Peanut, the pregnancy & mum app connecting women from fertility to menopause.

Over 5 million mums have joined Peanut to connect with other mum friends, ask questions, and find support. Whether you’re navigating pregnancy, mum loneliness, or menopause symptoms, the app provides access to a community of mums and mums-to-be ready to share advice.

Finding pregnancy and mum friends at a similar stage in life is easy on Peanut!

**FIND MUM FRIENDS WHO GET IT**

👋 Meet: Swipe to meet local mums at every life stage from pregnancy to menopause.

💬 Chat: Match with a new friend and talk via chat or video call, whether it's about your pregnancy, baby advice, or mum hacks.

👭 Groups: Join support groups for pregnancy, newborn baby care, toddler mums, and many more.

🫶🏼 Bump Buddies: Track pregnancy milestones with friends due around the same time.

🤔 Ask: Seek advice on baby names, pregnancy issues, and more from your new friends.

💁‍♀️ Share: Share advice across pregnancy, mum life, baby care, and more. Discuss topics like pregnancy sickness, baby name suggestions, baby hiccups, newborn routines, and other milestones in your mum journey.

👻 Incognito Mode: Ask anything anonymously. From sex during pregnancy, or how to deal with baby tantrums to the struggles of being a single mum.

**WE’VE GOT YOU**

Safety is embedded throughout the app to encourage caring, supportive, and purposeful connections among mums and women.

✔️ All profiles on Peanut are checked with selfie verification to ensure safety for all mums.

✔️ Zero tolerance for abusive behaviour.

✔️ Sensitive content filters mask content that may be triggering, protecting mums during pregnancy and beyond.

✔️ Customise your feed for pregnancy, baby care, or finding mum friends.

**WORD ON THE STREET**

🏆 Fast Company’s Most Innovative Companies 2023

🏆 TIME100’s Most Influential Companies 2022

🏆 Apple’s Trend of the Year 2021

📰 “The matchmaking app for modern mums” - Forbes

📰 “A welcoming community where everyone can have their say

, from pregnancy to menopause” - HuffPost

📰 "An app for any mum who missed out on dating apps” - New York Times

Welcome to Peanut, the pregnancy & mum app connecting women from fertility to menopause.

Over 5 million mums have joined Peanut to connect with other mum friends, ask questions, and find support. Whether you’re navigating pregnancy, mum loneliness, or menopause symptoms, the app provides access to a community of mums and mums-to-be ready to share advice.

Finding pregnancy and mum friends at a similar stage in life is easy on Peanut!

**FIND MUM FRIENDS WHO GET IT**

👋 Meet: Swipe to meet local mums at every life stage from pregnancy to menopause.

💬 Chat: Match with a new friend and talk via chat or video call, whether it's about your pregnancy, baby advice, or mum hacks.

👭 Groups: Join support groups for pregnancy, newborn baby care, toddler mums, and many more.

🫶🏼 Bump Buddies: Track pregnancy milestones with friends due around the same time.

🤔 Ask: Seek advice on baby names, pregnancy issues, and more from your new friends.

💁‍♀️ Share: Share advice across pregnancy, mum life, baby care, and more. Discuss topics like pregnancy sickness, baby name suggestions, baby hiccups, newborn routines, and other milestones in your mum journey.

👻 Incognito Mode: Ask anything anonymously. From sex during pregnancy, or how to deal with baby tantrums to the struggles of being a single mum.

**WE’VE GOT YOU**

Safety is embedded throughout the app to encourage caring, supportive, and purposeful connections among mums and women.

✔️ All profiles on Peanut are checked with selfie verification to ensure safety for all mums.

✔️ Zero tolerance for abusive behaviour.

✔️ Sensitive content filters mask content that may be triggering, protecting mums during pregnancy and beyond.

✔️ Customise your feed for pregnancy, baby care, or finding mum friends.

**WORD ON THE STREET**

🏆 Fast Company’s Most Innovative Companies 2023

🏆 TIME100’s Most Influential Companies 2022

🏆 Apple’s Trend of the Year 2021

📰 “The matchmaking app for modern mums” - Forbes

📰 “A welcoming community where everyone can have their say

, from pregnancy to menopause” - HuffPost

📰 "An app for any mum who missed out on dating apps” - New York Times

—————————————————————————————————

Peanut is free to download and use. If you're looking to speed up the friend-finding process, you can purchase a Peanut Plus subscription or keep swiping to find mum friends for free. The prices may vary per country and are clearly displayed in the app.

Privacy Policy: https://www.peanut-app.io/privacy

Terms of Use: https://www.peanut-app.io/terms

Community Guidelines: https://www.peanut-app.io/community-guidelines

App Support: feedback@teampeanut.com
descriptionShort: Meet like-minded mums anytime, anywhere.

Loving Peanut? Send us some love back with a five-star review! 🌟 It helps us grow our community and create a better experience for you.

With love,
Team Peanut 🥜
